<div class="allianceSection collapsable collapsed">
	 <h4 class="header">Fire Characteristics</h4>
	<div class="text"><i>Artemisia nova </i>is fire sensitive; fire is not a regular component of the alliance’s disturbance regime.</div>
	<table class="zebraStripe">
		
		<tr>
